query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 q1 s t1 tq1 b) NoHashJoin(a1 b q1 s t1 tq1 u1) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 0 AND q1.view_count <= 100
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('ajax',
'banco-de-dados',
'c#',
'electromagnetism',
'electrostatics',
'jquery',
'json',
'laravel',
'linux',
'quantum-field-theory',
'thermodynamics',
'база-данных',
'регулярные-выражения')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('physics',
'pt',
'ru',
'salesforce',
'serverfault')
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name IN ('Suffrage',
'Talkative')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 10 AND u1.reputation <= 100000
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
